metadata.name: Golden GM 2023
metadata.description:
This GM is for the NFT community who has supported me in the past 1.5 years. 
I want to give positive vibrations back in the form of a Lucky-charm for the next Bull Run. 
It's a GM of Abundance and Prosperity, GM of trust and support. We should lead each other step by step, walk the path of Success and Create a golden path Built on blockchain for the long term.  
GM because we are still early.  
A sun shining morning is coming because this is still the dawn of the Digital renaissance.

14 second video 3000x1750 pix.
